      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I'm working with a group of senior execs who are prepping for some really high-stakes board meetings and investor pitches. I want to give them some guidance on grooming and personal presentation to make sure they look as authoritative and professional as possible. What are some general rules or best practices for appearance in a high-level corporate setting?",
